f
x=(x_1,\dots,x_n)
df(x)=\frac{\partial f}{\partial x_1}dx_1+\sum_{i=2}^n \frac{\partial f}{\partial x_i} d x_i=\sum_{i=1}^n \frac{\partial f}{\partial x_i} d x_i=\langle \nabla f(x), dx \rangle 
dx=(dx_1,\dots,dx_n)
